private void ensureSaveEnvironment() throws Exception {
    SaveManager saveManager = new SaveManager(context, game);
    if (!saveManager.isPrefixReady()) {
        saveManager.setupPrefix();
    }
}
```

Ø«Ù… ÙÙŠ `launch()`:

```java
